{"tid":1330092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘鉉離世1年半　太妍IG留言「好想你…」","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T02:52:35.000Z","uid":213300,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd896645251ef2b4b8f5bcd1ca46351211ab708","tid":1330092,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"鐘鉉離世1年半 太妍IG留言「好想你&hellip;」粉絲淚崩<br />\n<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓歌手金鐘鉉在2017年底因憂鬱症輕生離世，令粉絲和眾多好友錯愕又傷心，女團「少<br />\n女時代」成員太妍和他情同姐弟，多次在IG發文透露失去摯友的悲痛，近日有粉絲發現，<br />\n太妍17日上午在鐘鉉過往的IG貼文下留言，雖然只是簡短的一句話，卻道盡了對好友的思<br />\n念之情。<br />\n<br />\n太妍和鐘鉉是SM娛樂公司的前後輩，在南韓演藝圈中是出了名的感情好，同是主唱的兩人<br />\n多次在音樂上交流，除了合唱歌曲《Breath》外，鐘鉉還曾為太妍量身打造《Lonely》，<br />\n而在鐘鉉逝世的噩耗傳出後，太妍不僅取消個人簽名會，還前往醫院守靈，告別式當日也<br />\n與好友們一起送他最後一程，並曾在IG發文哀悼好友，之後也不時貼文分享與鐘鉉過往有<br />\n趣的互動，不難看出對好友離世的不捨和悲痛。<br />\n<br />\n日前太妍親口坦承自己患有憂鬱症並努力接受治療，令粉絲們擔心不已，不過眼尖的粉絲<br />\n發現，近日較少更新IG的太妍17日在鐘鉉2017年11月20日的最後一篇IG貼文下留言「好想<br />\n你，我們鐘鉉啊」，簡短的一句話卻道盡了對好友的思念之情。<br />\n<br />\n鐘鉉逝世1年多，他最後一篇IG貼文每天仍有許多粉絲留言悼念，而太妍也並非首次在這<br />\n則貼文下留言，這次再度被發現，許多粉絲忍不住淚崩回應「和姐姐一樣，我也真的好想<br />\n念鐘鉉，我們永遠不會忘記他的」；也有不少人鼓勵太妍「想著鐘鉉，健康幸福的好好過<br />\n日子」、「姐姐也要保重自己，我們愛你」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pse.is/K72HV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2FK72HV&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=d2c1a7aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pse.is/K72HV</a><br />\n<br />\n▲太妍在鐘鉉IG留言「好想你，我們鐘鉉」。"},{"pid":"49d061bf688bc95adb663a26190590762d1f40b2","tid":1330092,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"R.I.P🙏"},{"pid":"5e93ef785fb159f848d6ff9ed188645c14af125f","tid":1330092,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112f033bb2d72179fed4c4eb30a794a5dc11c06d","tid":1330092,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"how to be happy"},{"pid":"ccf119815a50c9845648cf3869f0870f4505f47e","tid":1330092,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"撲哥sip噠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0bb0b516d520b113a64578babd4db0c8bbb9b8","tid":1330092,"uid":240608,"like":9,"dislike":18,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"又博曝光率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54318c9b8a0262279a42d271002805cfcdd35c8","tid":1330092,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"諗起yeri"},{"pid":"c9f1924cc14581e4f9b120a89ed398a6838c9cea","tid":1330092,"uid":238483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"樓主準備睇邊仔洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38255d0cc6bd9d2c2030e68f870e41da3e67f0b4","tid":1330092,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"食屎吧泰妍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318a809f85d669cb04ffd09e2e719add69ee7aa5","tid":1330092,"uid":170294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:58:28.000Z","msg":"泰研唱歌係幾好聽 (唔係飯佢)"},{"pid":"d88c65c0c99eca916947a15ff981de518daa9afd","tid":1330092,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9f1924cc14581e4f9b120a89ed398a6838c9cea","tid":1330092,"uid":238483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"樓主準備睇邊仔洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}